<HEADLINE> Netherlands Beats Yugoslavia 6-1 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, June 25 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results of the
Netherlands-Yugoslavia quarter-final match at the 2000 European
championship at the Feyenoord Stadium in Rotterdam of the
Netherlands on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Netherlands beat Yugoslavia 6-1 (halftime 2-0)
</P>
<P>
Scorers:
</P>
<P>
Netherlands - Patrick Kluivert 24, 38, 51, 54, Marc Overmars 78,
90
</P>
<P>
Yugoslavia - Savo Milosevic 90
</P>
<P>
Halftime: 2-0; Attendance: 44,000
</P>
<P>
Teams:
</P>
<P>
Netherlands: 1-Edwin van der Sar (22-Sander Westerveld 65);15-
Paul Bosvelt, 3-Jaap Stam, 4-Frank de Boer (captain),19-Arthur
Numan; 5-Boudewijn Zenden (Ronald De Boer 80), 8-Edgar Davids, 7-
Phillip Cocu, 11-Marc Overmars; 10-Dennis Bergkamp,9-Patrick
Kluivert (21-Roy Makaay 60).
</P>
<P>
Yugoslavia: 22-Ivica Kralj; 11-Sinisa Mihajlovic,13-Slobodan
Komljenovic, 14-Nisa Saveljic (19-Jovan Stankovic 56), 5-Miroslav
Djukic; 7-Vladimir Jugovic, 10-Dragan Stojkovic(captain, 6-Dejan
Stankovic 53), 16-Dejan Govedarica,17-Ljubinko Drulovic (18-Darko
Kovacevic 70); 8-Predrag Mijatovic, 9-Savo Milosevic.
</P>
<P>
Referee: Jose Maria Garcia-Aranda, Spain
</P>
