<DOCNO> XIE20000626.0018 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-26 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
