<HEADLINE> Jordan`s Stock Market Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, June 26 (Xinhua) -- The price index of Jordan`s Amman
Financial Market closed at 143.58 on Monday, 0.35 points lower than
Sunday`s finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 879,817 Jordanian dinars (1.23 million U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 435,400 shares changed hands in 467 deals. 
</P>
