<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, June 26 (Xinhua) -- Li Peng, Chairman of the Standing
Committee of China's National People's Congress (NPC), met here
Monday with Chairman of the Ukrainian Supreme Council, Ivan
Plyushch, on bilateral ties, cooperation between the two
parliaments and the international situation.
</P>
