Li expressed his gratitude and appreciation for Ukraine's right
stand and its support to China on the issues of human rights,
Taiwan and Tibet.
</P>
<P>
Plyushch held a welcome banquet in honor of Li Peng and his
wife Zhu Lin after the talks. 
