<HEADLINE> Gold Price Down in Hong Kong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 26 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong lost
8 HK dollars to close at 2,620 HK dollars a tael Monday, according
to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 282.45 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, down 0.89 U.S. dollars from the previous trading session at
Monday's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7855 HK
dollars. 
</P>
