<P>
He said "Turkey is on the main road of heroin traffic. Seventy
percent of the Afghan heroin arrives in Europe passing through
Turkey. The income of the Turkish mafia from this traffic reaches
billions of U.S. dollars." 
</P>
</TEXT>
