<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE20000626.0342 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-26 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 23 Kilograms of Drugs Seized in Pakistan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Quoting ANF sources, the report said that in pursuance of its
task to eliminate the narcotics business, ANF got an information
that the drugs were being transported from Tribal Area through oil
tankers to Karachi for onward dispatch to European Countries via
Arabian sea.
</P>
<P>
A surveillance of the area was carried out which revealed that
some bags, including 23 kilograms of heroin, 28 kilograms of opium
paste and 31 kilograms of hsshish, had been suspiciously dumped in
the bushes near the basin. 
</P>
