<HEADLINE> Colombia Paramilitary Murder Six People </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Members of the right-wing United Autodefenses of Colombia (AUC)
shot three peasants at La Estacion de Angelopolis country house,
after accusing them of backing guerrillas.
</P>
<P>
In a second event in Los Mojones de Armenia village,
paramilitary took out, list in hand, two people from their
dwellings and killed them, as well as at country house El
Diamnante, where another peasant in AUC hands was shot.
</P>
<P>
According to official reports, extreme-right groups
assassinated over 1,000 civilians last year, most of them peasants
accused of collaborating with guerrillas. 
</P>
</TEXT>
