first quarter totaled a record 62.7 billion dollars.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, U.S. investors acquired nearly 15.8 billion of
foreign stock in the first quarter, the largest quarterly total
since second quarter of 1996, marking the third consecutive
quarter of net purchases of foreign securities by U.S. investors,
the SIA said in its Foreign Activity Report. 
